      "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/5d4e9fa4-6890-11e3-a9a3-52540035b04c).  Ran 19 tests.  No failures.",
